### BoardBuddies Board API Collection
### Board 도메인 관련 API 요청들

### Create a board game
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/boards
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Monopoly",
  "description": "Classic board game",
  "minPlayers": 2,
  "maxPlayers": 6,
  "category": "STRATEGY"
}

### Get board game by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/boards/1

### Get all board games
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/boards

### Update board game
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/boards/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Monopoly Deluxe",
  "description": "Enhanced classic board game",
  "minPlayers": 2,
  "maxPlayers": 8,
  "category": "STRATEGY"
}

### Delete board game
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/boards/1

### Search boards by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/boards/search?category=STRATEGY
